Ngayong gabi ang gabi ng aming kasal.

00:41:15.360 --> 00:41:16.590
saan ka pupunta

00:41:17.880 --> 00:41:18.880
Pareho kaming pagod.

00:41:19.800 --> 00:41:20.640
Magpahinga na tayo ng maaga.

00:41:24.960 --> 00:41:26.760
Hindi ako kailanman kumapit sa nakaraan.

00:41:27.440 --> 00:41:28.280
paano mo malalaman

00:41:28.760 --> 00:41:29.840
Dumating ako para sayo?

00:41:30.920 --> 00:41:31.760
Ngayong araw

00:41:31.760 --> 00:41:32.960
naparito ako para sa

00:41:32.960 --> 00:41:33.960
Batang Heneral Wei Jun.

00:41:44.660 --> 00:41:48.220
(Marquis ng Zhenguo's Mansion)

00:41:52.140 --> 00:41:59.140
(Sa Pines and Bamboos)

00:42:44.710 --> 00:42:45.550
Kuya Wei,

00:42:47.000 --> 00:42:47.840
patawarin mo ako

00:42:47.850 --> 00:42:48.880
para sa pagpasok sa sambahayan ni Wei

00:42:48.880 --> 00:42:49.840
sa ganitong paraan.

00:42:51.590 --> 00:42:52.630
Ang bagay na ito ay maaaring

00:42:52.630 --> 00:42:54.030
graver kaysa sa naisip namin.

00:42:55.440 --> 00:42:56.320
Ngunit ipinapangako ko sa iyo,

00:42:57.230 --> 00:42:58.590
sa sandaling matuklasan ko ang katotohanan,

00:42:59.800 --> 00:43:01.030
Aalis na ako at aaminin ko ang kasalanan ko

00:43:01.440 --> 00:43:02.280
sarili ko.

00:43:03.880 --> 00:43:04.720
